{"tid":1564720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[藍絲最嬲的畫面]今個星期個youtube熱門終於正常返","createTime":"2019-09-13T01:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T10:25:14.000Z","uid":36788,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fbbfda13723c752e34a2dfdc4e87972098d3924e","tid":1564720,"uid":36788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:20:08.000Z","msg":"屌上星期都係咩暴徒亂港，見到就忟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個星期既排版好治癒又振奮人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45UqRAU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45UqRAU.png&h=72b535e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好俾佢停<br />\nyoutube係好重要既文宣戰線<br />\n好多藍絲唔識subscribe只會睇熱門"},{"pid":"aa54991af2da7f2c5f1bb6c5e5552b4ca58850aa","tid":1564720,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:21:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"be57f86c8a430289a9fe7f283cc338ee6d5d520b","tid":1564720,"uid":60716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:24:26.000Z","msg":"管弦樂MV 呢個係原創者？"},{"pid":"3aaf3f3ddcf1ea55e8e54fd8e81b992dac1f5563","tid":1564720,"uid":